cacheTempView(sql="
SELECT
  DISTINCT atb.orderDate,
  atb.utmContent,
  atb.orderId,
  atb.subOrderId,
  ftu.guid,
  ag.shippedStatus,
  ag.statusCode,
  atb.deviceType,
  ue.NMIncAd
FROM(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT orderDate,
      orderId,
      subOrderId,
      deviceType,
      utmContent
    FROM
      `temp.attributedOrders`
    WHERE
      (
        orderDate in ('2023-04-24','2023-04-25','2023-04-26','2023-04-27','2023-04-28','2023-04-29','2023-04-30')
      )
      AND lower(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%plfeed%'
      AND lower(utmContent) NOT LIKE '%testns1%'
  ) atb
  LEFT JOIN(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT guid,
      orderId
    FROM
      `temp.shippedFTUs`
  ) ftu ON atb.orderId = ftu.orderId
  LEFT JOIN(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT subOrderId,
      shippedStatus,
      statusCode
    FROM
      `all(agCmDump)`
  ) ag ON atb.subOrderId = ag.subOrderId
  LEFT JOIN(
    SELECT
      DISTINCT subOrderId,
      NMIncAd
    FROM
      `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)`
  ) ue ON atb.subOrderId = ue.subOrderId

","temp.content_rawData_1")
